claim.claim-text:
A wind turbine comprising:
- a nacelle (200) having a main frame (205);
- a hub provided with blades and rotatably mounted to the nacelle (200); and
- a tower (215) rotatably supporting the nacelle (200);
wherein it further comprises at least one rotating assembly (100) as claimed in any of the preceding claims for rotation of the nacelle main frame (205) relative to the tower (215).
